Package main.java.persistence.databaseTables

Interface AbstractEntry

All Known Implementing Classes:
Addresses, Assignees, ChangesOfAddresses, HouseOwners, HouseProviders, Identifications, Persons, Processes, StagesOfCOA
public interface AbstractEntry
This interfaces only purpose is to act as parent for all table classes. With this the DatabaseManager can be protected from classes that aren't supposed to be stored in the DB.
